# Tracked snapshots — current state of paper-trading experiment.
# These get noisy in git status (bot rewrites every save cycle), but the
# user wants them committed so progress is visible and analysis is reproducible.
!bot-data/arena_results.json
!bot-data/live_validator.json
!bot-data/council.json
!bot-data/watchdog.json
!bot-data/strategy_blacklist.json
!bot-data/walkforward_results.json
!bot-data/mass_backtest_metavote.json
!bot-data/phase3_obi_results.json
!bot-data/daily_report_*.md

# Bot credentials (MUST NOT be committed)
.env.bot
.env.*.bot

